GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 21st December, 2013

The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 21st December, 2013:
(i)
Minister of State (Independent Charge) of the Ministry of Environment and
Forests; and
Smt. Jayanthi Natarajan relinquished the charge of the office of the
(ii)
Shri M. Veerappa Moily, Minister of Petroleum and Natural Gas assumed
the additional charge of the office of the Minster of Environment and Forests.
(K.L. Sharma)
